channel.title: How do i play on other servers with other people on moparscape?
channel.description: i need some help with getting onto other servers with real people. can someone help me with all the downloads? i have moparscape download of course but what else do i need to be able to play with others im despret!!!!!! :confused:

item.title: How do i play on other servers with other people on moparscape?
item.dc:creator: @Informer Informer
item.description:
@Informer wrote:

Go to the “help” on the client then go to “server status” then copy the server ip and port then go back to the client and go to “file” then click on New server then paste the server ip with ctrl+v or just type it then go to “file” again on the client and click on new port and write the port#'s witch is mostly 43594.

Enjoy,happy gaming!
